typan-war-guide-title = Station War
typan-war-guide-body =
    T+0 — war declared, bluespace jumps blocked until hostilities begin.
    T+5 min — hostilities begin, war armories unlock (TypanWarArmory tag).
    30 min — combat timer; win by fewer losses or total elimination.
    Ally Protection — do not hit allies with ranged weapons.
